"title": "7755: preaching, importance of",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "7755",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>Preaching has a central place among God's people and is vital to their life and growth. It is authorised by God, empowered by the Holy Spirit and expressed supremely by Jesus Christ.</p>\n<h2>Preaching has its origin in God</h2>\n<h3>It is a divine command</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark16:15\">MRK 16:15</a></strong> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt28:18-Matt28:20\">MAT 28:18–28:20</a> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jonah1:1-Jonah1:2\">JON 1:1–1:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt10:5-Matt10:7\">MAT 10:5–10:7</a> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark6:7-Mark6:12\">MRK 6:7–6:12</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke9:1-Luke9:6\">LUK 9:1–9:6</a></p>\n<h3>It is rooted in God's grace</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph3:7-Eph3:9\">EPH 3:7–3:9</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa6:1-Isa6:10\">ISA 6:1–6:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom15:15-Rom15:16\">ROM 15:15–15:16</a></p>\n<h3>It is empowered by God's Spirit</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts1:8\">ACT 1:8</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa61:1-Isa61:3\">ISA 61:1–61:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke24:46-Luke24:49\">LUK 24:46–24:49</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts2:1-Acts2:11\">ACT 2:1–2:11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts4:8-Acts4:12\">ACT 4:8–4:12</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts10:44\">ACT 10:44</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor2:4-1Cor2:5\">1CO 2:4–2:5</a></p>\n<h2>The importance of preaching and Jesus Christ</h2>\n<h3>Jesus Christ himself came to preach</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark1:38\">MRK 1:38</a></strong> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke4:43\">LUK 4:43</a> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph2:17\">EPH 2:17</a></p>\n<h3>Jesus Christ's own ministry involved much preaching</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt4:23\">MAT 4:23</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt11:1-Matt11:5\">MAT 11:1–11:5</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke7:18-Luke7:22\">LUK 7:18–7:22</a></p>\n<h3>Jesus Christ commissioned his disciples to preach</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark3:14-Mark3:15\">MRK 3:14–3:15</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt10:5-Matt10:7\">MAT 10:5–10:7</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke9:1-Luke9:2\">LUK 9:1–9:2</a></p>\n<h2>The importance of preaching and the church</h2>\n<h3>It is a natural part of the church's life</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts8:4\">ACT 8:4</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts3:11-Acts3:26\">ACT 3:11–3:26</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts15:35\">ACT 15:35</a></p>\n<h3>It is a trust from God</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal2:7\">GAL 2:7</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Thess2:4\">1TH 2:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Tim1:11\">1TI 1:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Titus1:3\">TIT 1:3</a></p>\n<h3>It is an integral aspect of key ministries in the church</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Tim3:2\">1TI 3:2</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph4:11-Eph4:12\">EPH 4:11–4:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Tim4:2-2Tim4:5\">2TI 4:2–4:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Titus1:7-Titus1:9\">TIT 1:7–1:9</a></p>\n<h3>Its importance to Paul</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor1:17-1Cor1:18\">1CO 1:17–1:18</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts9:20-Acts9:22\">ACT 9:20–9:22</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts18:5\">ACT 18:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom1:14-Rom1:15\">ROM 1:14–1:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor1:22-1Cor1:25\">1CO 1:22–1:25</a></p>\n<h3>It is an apostolic command</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Tim4:13\">1TI 4:13</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Tim4:2\">2TI 4:2</a></p>\n<h2>The importance of preaching for salvation</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom10:14-Rom10:15\">ROM 10:14–10:15</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa52:7\">ISA 52:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom10:17\">ROM 10:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor1:21\">1CO 1:21</a></p>\n<h2>The importance of preaching means preachers and teachers will be judged more strictly</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas3:1\">JAS 3:1</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom2:17-Rom2:24\">ROM 2:17–2:24</a></p>",
